daedcb79bcb483f96214be190d7d1f02be8aef86.commitMessage:
New file cleaner that keeps track of files pending deletion, and deletes
them only when an associated marker object is reclaimed by the garbage
collector. This class avoids the need to use File.deleteOnExit() in a
server environment.

Obtained from: Noel Bergman
